cfdm.AuxiliaryCoordinate.insert_data¶

AuxiliaryCoordinate.insert_data(data, bounds=None, copy=True)¶

Insert a new data array.

A bounds data array may also inserted if given with the bounds keyword. Bounds may also be inserted independently with the insert_bounds method.

New in version 2.0.

Parameters:

data : Data

bounds : Data, optional

copy : bool, optional
Returns:

None
